noria:TTPI_ISPContacted a noria:Property ;
    rdfs:label "ISP Contacted"@en ;
    rdfs:comment "Intervention record: ISP A was contacted at 10:15 AM."@en .

# Connect Anomaly Patterns to potential causes or related events
